div.div: MASHLE: Kami Shinkakusha Kouho Senbatsu Shiken-hen
The second season of MASHLE, adapting the Divine Visionary Candidate Exam Arc.

How can you fall in love when you cant even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will diewhich makes his flirty maids behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

Gorou is a gynecologist and idol fan whos in shock after his favorite star, Ai, announces an impromptu hiatus. Little does Gorou realize that hes about to forge a bond with her that defies all common sense! Lies are an idols weapon! (Source: Yen Press)

Awards:

- Winner of the 7th Next Manga Award in the print category.
- Nominated for the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize.
- Nominated for the 67th Shogakukan Manga Award in general category.
- Nominated for the 46th Kodansha Manga Award.
